sequenceDiagram
    actor Dev as Developer
    participant IDE as IDE/Agent
    participant VDB as Vector DB
    participant LLM as LLM
    
    Dev->>IDE: "refactor the login service to use the new JWT library"
    IDE->>IDE: Convert request into a numerical vector (an "embedding")
    IDE->>VDB: Similarity search against the indexed codebase
    VDB-->>IDE: Most semantically relevant chunks of code and docs
    IDE->>IDE: Augment the original prompt with retrieved chunks
    IDE->>LLM: Curated prompt (instruction + augmented context)
    LLM-->>IDE: Response (proposed diff + rationale)
    IDE-->>Dev: Patch with explanation